                            <comment id="12543907" author="jukkaz" created="Tue, 20 Nov 2007 14:39:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I would rather have the Appendable-&amp;gt;ContentHandler mapping happening through an adapter class for maximum separation of concerns, but that&apos;s a minor issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12543944" author="niallp" created="Tue, 20 Nov 2007 16:51:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes thats probably better - attaching v2 of the patch which include an adaptor. Note the ApendableAdaptorTest needs a new &quot;sax&quot; directory in the test source. My svn client isn&apos;t doing new directories for some reason.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12545306" author="jukkaz" created="Sun, 25 Nov 2007 22:52:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch (v2) committed in revision 598075. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
